          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Milestone updates</li>
